<div id="completeWishModal" class="fixed inset-0 hidden z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-40"></div>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl w-full max-w-md text-center p-8 relative z-10 shadow-xl">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <svg class="mx-auto w-12 h-12 text-purple-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
      Вітаємо!
    </h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
      Ви щойно виконали бажання: <span id="completeWishTitle" class="font-semibold text-purple-700"></span><br>
      Бажаємо, щоб збувалося ще більше!
    </p>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Дата виконання</label>
      <input type="date" id="completionDate"
        class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent">
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-3">
      <button onclick="confirmCompleteWish()"
        class="flex-1 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors">
        Позначити виконаним
      </button>
      <button onclick="closeCompleteWishModal()"
        class="flex-1 bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors">
        Скасувати
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>